<span id="freeTextContainer7199023705243160952">The Shadow Girl is a young adult novel but it&apos;s written from a grown up point in the main character&apos;s life so both young and old can enjoy it. If you&apos;ve never struggled with anxiety you will definitely understand it better after reading this book. The whole novel has a creepy, mysterious vibe that even gave me goosebumps at some places. The main character, Zylia was so easy for me to love. She has a funny, awkward and downright endearing personality. I&apos;d recommend this book to anyone who loves d</span>
  <span id="freeText7199023705243160952" style="display:none">The Shadow Girl is a young adult novel but it's written from a grown up point in the main character's life so both young and old can enjoy it. If you've never struggled with anxiety you will definitely understand it better after reading this book. The whole novel has a creepy, mysterious vibe that even gave me goosebumps at some places. The main character, Zylia was so easy for me to love. She has a funny, awkward and downright endearing personality. I'd recommend this book to anyone who loves drama with a splash of mystery and fantasy. I loved this story so much, I hope there will be a sequel!<br /></span>
