<span id="freeTextContainer7558932010931865570">&quot;I read because my grandmother showed me how to immerse myself in books for recreation, relaxation or even as a coping skill.<br/><br/>I write because my head is filled with daydreams and I like to choose the endings.&quot;<br/><br/>Misty Mount has written since age five and was first published at fourteen. By day she&apos;s a caregiver, wife, and mother to a young son but during the quiet hours of night she becomes a novelist</span>
  <span id="freeText7558932010931865570" style="display:none">"I read because my grandmother showed me how to immerse myself in books for recreation, relaxation or even as a coping skill.<br /><br />I write because my head is filled with daydreams and I like to choose the endings."<br /><br />Misty Mount has written since age five and was first published at fourteen. By day she's a caregiver, wife, and mother to a young son but during the quiet hours of night she becomes a novelist.</span>
